{"tid":1797661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕後好想再發夢","createTime":"2019-12-25T15:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:00:25.000Z","uid":169261,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2e1b4b450562a24c5f4597db9b54c7c22dda56","tid":1797661,"uid":169261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:32:11.000Z","msg":"小弟被狗咬過。<br />\n衰d咩我唔講啦廢事自爆<br />\n其實諗過退game，但係見到緊排勇武手足真係越黎越少<br />\n各位都見到聖誕節係旺角彌敦道同細街係平行時空<br />\n小弟見宜家咁嘅形勢真係好想繼續發夢<br />\n<br />\n再者如果之後有大日子，真係唔想有得其他手足係街到發夢自己又係屋企咩都唔做。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己會好心up，覺得自己好懦夫</span><br />\n但再衰就荔枝角見。<br />\n唔想死得無價值<br />\n真係好撚矛盾<br />\n<br />\n有無人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfeb932ff1c51ef2d0f4f5d5cbe38b1287c1fe4","tid":1797661,"uid":169261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"推三下<br />\n一"},{"pid":"0df6d7d2e858ee130d47226fa22d0d6e90d3ac8a","tid":1797661,"uid":169261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"7e867610575be89bc7009fd5f2c35328e15b5dd6","tid":1797661,"uid":169261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"1979df1f0433f2cd9fb03bf8a28c03c19821f235","tid":1797661,"uid":319824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a348c7d45d4ca244357e328dd494bb2e8e9071a","tid":1797661,"uid":191733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:33:39.000Z","msg":"如果被捕，就唔好再上嚟，放心大家會撐你"},{"pid":"4ac086a709b3b0bdbe09e25de7669f974f1f2d99","tid":1797661,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"保釋唔好博  拎左黃要收下火 再黃就出埸<br />\n<br />\n<im